#. <section class="sutta" id="an3.89"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.89:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.89:0.2"
msgid "9. Samaṇavagga"
msgstr "9. Ascetics"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.89:0.3"
msgid "89. Paṭhamasikkhattayasutta"
msgstr "89. Three Trainings (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an3.89:1.1"
msgid "“Tisso imā, bhikkhave, sikkhā."
msgstr "“Mendicants, these are the three trainings."

msgctxt "an3.89:1.2"
msgid "Katamā tisso?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an3.89:1.3"
msgid "Adhisīlasikkhā, adhicittasikkhā, adhipaññāsikkhā."
msgstr ""
"The training in the higher ethics, the higher mind, and the higher wisdom."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an3.89:2.1"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, adhisīlasikkhā?"
msgstr "And what is the training in the higher ethics?"

msgctxt "an3.89:2.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlavā hoti … pe … samādāya sikkhati sikkhāpadesu."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant is ethical, restrained in the code of conduct, and has "
"appropriate behavior and means of collecting alms. Seeing danger in the "
"slightest flaw, they keep the rules they’ve undertaken."

msgctxt "an3.89:2.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, adhisīlasikkhā."
msgstr "This is called the training in the higher ethics."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an3.89:3.1"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, adhicittasikkhā?"
msgstr "And what is the training in the higher mind?"

msgctxt "an3.89:3.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu vivicceva kāmehi … pe … catutthaṃ jhānaṃ "
"upasampajja viharati."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant, quite secluded from sensual pleasures, secluded from "
"unskillful qualities, enters and remains in the first absorption … second "
"absorption … third absorption … fourth absorption."

msgctxt "an3.89:3.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, adhicittasikkhā."
msgstr "This is called the training in the higher mind."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an3.89:4.1"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, adhipaññāsikkhā?"
msgstr "And what is the training in the higher wisdom?"

msgctxt "an3.89:4.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti … pe … ‘ayaṃ "
"dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti."
msgstr ""
"They truly understand: ‘This is suffering’ … ‘This is the origin of "
"suffering’ … ‘This is the cessation of suffering’ … ‘This is the practice "
"that leads to the cessation of suffering’."

msgctxt "an3.89:4.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, adhipaññāsikkhā."
msgstr "This is called the training in the higher wisdom."

msgctxt "an3.89:4.4"
msgid "Imā kho, bhikkhave, tisso sikkhā”ti."
msgstr "These are the three trainings.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.89:4.5"
msgid "Navamaṃ."
msgstr ""
